The Justice League of America attend a convention on conserving electricity and meet some kids and tell the kids a story of why they should conserve electricity.

description:
As Spider-Man's Brand New Day rolls on, fan response to the bold new direction has been amazingly enthusiastic! Since there's so much to talk about in the world of Peter Parker, MARVEL SPOTLIGHT returns with a fresh look at the creators, new villains and snazzy new supporting cast that fill out Spidey's thrice-monthly adventures. Kraven and Venom lead the pack of a whole passel of vituperative villains returning to victimize Spider-Man, but it's the comeback of ace artist John Romita Jr. that'll have fans web-swinging from the rooftops! See ya in August with a brand-new Brand New Day SPOTLIGHT!

It's a "Brand New Day" with "New Ways to Die" as the Amazing Spider-Man swings his way headlong into the future... a future that features a wonderful mix of old and new! And this month's Spotlight is here to give you a close look!
name: Inside Brand New Day

description: Guilt-Na-Zan is a vampire aristocrat who was sealed into a cross by Kyouji's ancestor more than 100 years ago. Now Kyouji has revived him--although he was resurrected as a doll and can only transform into his real figure when he sucks blood from Kyouji's sister Tonae... But when you combine Goth clothes and hot vampires, slowly but surely everyone will start to feel like one big family!
name: Vol. 1

description: Guilt-Na hasn’t been feeling good lately. It seems the only person that may be able to help her is Kyouichi. After many failed attempts to restore Guilt-Na to normal, Mariya Hugo offers to work her magic. However, Mariya's magic comes at a price. Is Guilt-Na willing to pay for it?
name: Vol. 3

description: Guilt-Na explains to Vincent who he really is and why she keeps him as a servant. Meanwhile, Shizuka finds an impostor of Guilt-Na and Vincent. These impostors seem to be linked to Kyoichi and Kyoji. Kyoji has an unusual request for Guilt-Na on his birthday. Will she be able to do it for him?
name: Vol. 4

description: With trouble once again brewing at Tonae's school, it's up to Guilt-na to again go undercover and solve the mystery. But who is the devilish god of death who has appeared at Mitsuhatsu Academy to hunt down souls? And what business does he have with Guilt-na-Zan!
name: Vol. 5
Das Grosse Mad Handbuch fur den Kampf Gegen
